name: XAEA-Xii
description: The XÆA-XII Token (Son of Elon) will be the foundation for investors to buy, sell, and stake NFT's. The XÆA-XII Token will be listed on multiple exchanges for simple transactions and is the genesis for X-Mask Wallet (which will store Tokens and NFT's) and the entire XÆA-XII NFT Platform ecosystem. The XÆA-XII NFT Platform will in turn feed revenue back to the XÆA-XII Token.
